Package BobcatLib.Subsystems.Elevators.Modules

Class ElevatorModuleReal

java.lang.Object
BobcatLib.Subsystems.Elevators.Modules.ElevatorModuleReal
All Implemented Interfaces:
ElevatorModuleIO
public class ElevatorModuleReal extends Object implements ElevatorModuleIO
Implementation of the ElevatorModule interface for a real elevator module. Handles motor control, position tracking, and voltage control.
